text: Atzeneta d'Albaida () is a municipality in the comarca of Vall d'Albaida, in the province of Valencia, in the Valencian Community, Spain. ==Sights== * Church of Saint John the Baptist * Hermitage of Cristo del Calvario * Nevera de Dalt * Nevera de Baix (snow wells) == References == Category:Municipalities in the Province of Valencia Category:Vall d'Albaida
title: Atzeneta d'Albaida
